    We found some snakes up in Ssrazarah today, so we headed over there and killed the rune covered servant. The exiled popped immediately afterwards, who we proceeded to give a good beat down... until one of the clerics in the chain went LD. At that point all hell broke loose. Maintank died instantly, followed by the next tank getting DT'd right away. Almost got him, he'll die next time.<br><br><center>
<img src=http://home.worldonline.dk/~kingri/Screenshots/Exiled2.jpg></center><br><br>If you look real closely there, you can see Choupie practising feign death as a rogue.<br><br>
Not much of an update today, but I'm wasted. Blame corporal punishment.<br><br><br><b>Bernie adventure of the day!</b><br><br>
